====Verb====
{{zh-verb|ts}}

# [[think]] {{gloss|to conceive of something or someone}}
#* {{zh-usex|我 想 她 是 衰老 了。|I think she's going senile.}}
# to [[think]] about; to [[plan]]; to be [[considering]]
#* {{zh-usex|我 '''想''' 在 暑假 打工。|I'm '''planning''' to get a job for the summer.}}
# to [[think]]; to [[suppose]]; to [[guess]]; to [[reckon]]
#* {{zh-usex|我 想 我 能 給 你 找到 合適 的 尺碼。|I think I can find the right size for you.}}
# to [[want]]; to [[wish]] for; to [[desire]]
#* {{zh-usex|還 '''想''' 喝 一 杯 嗎？|Would you '''like''' another drink?}}
#* {{zh-usex|她 '''想''' 當 芭蕾舞 演員。|She '''wants''' to be a ballet dancer.}}
# to [[miss]] {{gloss|to feel the absence of someone or something}}
#* {{zh-usex|你 走 了 我 會 '''想''' 你 的。|I'll '''miss''' you when you're gone.}}

